overview.en: Bitchane describes itself as a DeFi project providing access to instant financing by allowing users to trade, lend, and borrow tokens directly from their wallets. Bitchane is built on the 0x protocol with future integration of the project's ERC20 token, chanecoin as a stablecoin and a governing asset/currency. Users around the world are able to participate in the network's governance and contribute to Bitchane.
